{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"copy"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray<MLNPolygon *>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"polygons"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/polygons"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"polygons","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPolygon(py)polygons","role":"symbol","title":"polygons","symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"polygons","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of polygons forming the multipolygon."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/polygons"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNMultiPolygon","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll: the inner island would be one "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon"},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolygon":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNPolygon","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a closed shape consisting of four or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertices, specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the edges that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon/polygons":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"polygons","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/polygons","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/polygons","abstract":[{"text":"An array of polygons forming the multipolygon.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"polygons"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic"}}}